SELECT
    Fecha AS "time",
    'Stu_01' AS "student",
    SUM(Stu_01 * `Peso_en_calif_final_(%)`) OVER (ORDER BY Fecha) AS "cumulative_weighted_score"
FROM
    Fecha
WHERE Tipo_actividad = "EJC";
